### SOVR Doctrine Compliance
- **Mechanical Truth Display**: All balances show "cleared obligations"
- **No Reversals Messaging**: Clear finality in all interfaces
- **Attestation-First Flow**: Attestation required before any action
- **External Honoring Optional**: Users can skip honoring agents

### Survival Testing Success
